message: ProgressCircular flat prop added and doc updated

Bump loader-utils and react-scripts

Bumps [loader-utils](https://github.com/webpack/loader-utils) to 1.4.2 and updates ancestor dependency [react-scripts](https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app/tree/HEAD/packages/react-scripts). These dependencies need to be updated together.
